<p>&#8216;Victims of modern slavery are to receive better support in prison following a legal challenge which highlighted a lack of guidance for prison staff. The new guidance, to be issued later this year, will help prison staff support victims and potential victims of modern slavery who have been imprisoned under criminal powers.&#8217;</p>
<p><a href="https://eachother.org.uk/new-guidance-will-help-modern-slavery-victims-in-prison/">Full Story</a></p><p>Each Other, 4th August 2022</p><p>Source: <a href="https://eachother.org.uk">eachother.org.uk</a></p>